<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="hr">
<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8">
  <title>Razina 2 – Skriveno na vidljivom</title>
</head>
<body style="font-family: sans-serif; padding: 40px; max-width: 800px; margin: auto; text-align: center;">
  <h1>🔍 Dobrodošao na Razinu 2</h1>

  <p>Na ovoj stranici se skriva flag – možeš li ga pronaći?</p>
  <p><em>Nešto je skriveno... ali ipak prisutno 👁️</em></p>

  <form method="POST" style="margin-top: 30px;">
    <input type="text" name="flag" placeholder="Unesi flag" required
           style="padding: 10px; font-size: 16px; width: 250px;" />
    <button type="submit" style="padding: 10px 20px; font-size: 16px;">Pošalji</button>
  </form>

  <% if (error) { %>
    <p style="color: red; margin-top: 20px;"><%= error %></p>
  <% } %>

  <!-- Hm... što je ovo? 🤔 -->
  <input type="hidden" value="flag{hidden_but_not_safe}" />

  <hr style="margin: 40px auto; width: 60%;" />

  <img src="https://media4.giphy.com/media/v1.Y2lkPTc5MGI3NjExOGJremJ4dzYwdXM0NjZvdTdkaTVuYjFpZTJ4ajIzenppZW92aXZ2ZCZlcD12MV9pbnRlcm5hbF9naWZfYnlfaWQmY3Q9Zw/PadfCrnNVQzozq6A0m/giphy.gif"
     alt="Skriveno prisutno" style="max-width: 100%; border-radius: 8px;" />


  <p style="margin-top: 10px; color: gray;">
    💡 Hint: Ponekad su <strong>skrivene vrijednosti</strong> još uvijek dio stranice. 
  </p>
</body>
</html>
